data.description: PRICE IMPROVED., quick move in.   This lovely home is like brand new.  New LVP flooring throughout, new custom doors, trim, cabinets, granite countertops,  porches,  and HVAC. This home also boasts a conditioned crawl space, backyard fencing, and underground pet fencing all around.   Beautiful 3+ acre lot with something for everyone.  3 outbuildings with potential of "she shed/man cave",  huge garage and workspace for the handyman., and a lovely terrace with gazebo to enjoy the outdoors.  Buildings all have garage doors for easy access.  The quality of this home and the beauty of its location make it a must see.
